{"tid":736462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"憂得罪中國　西方不敢公開批評","createTime":"2018-07-10T09:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T09:23:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ae0a93d1aec825e59fa73f6554f612a9e81410","tid":736462,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:09:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180710/20445646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180710%2F20445646&d=yJ2kETKxjOjjyTvR2w%2FLZDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=43bf0cc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180710%2F20445646&h=d93a6a44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180710/20445646</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月10日 <br />\n<br />\n憂得罪中國　西方不敢公開批評<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180710/large/16613019.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180710%2Flarge%2F16613019.jpg&h=383928c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■劉霞被中共軟禁多年，至今未獲自由。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「民間及政府力量做足的話，劉曉波不會這樣死在獄中。我們大家都有責任，責無旁貸！」諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波去年因肝癌於獄中病逝，至死才得自由。國際特赦組織研究員潘嘉偉批評西方政府營救劉霞不力，要求西方政府公開施壓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180710/large/a0102a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180710%2Flarge%2Fa0102a.gif&h=97fc0e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n國際特赦組織籲施壓<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織研究員潘嘉偉指，北京一直以劉霞的弟弟劉暉作要脅，指劉霞可以出國，但劉暉要留下來成為人質，以免劉霞在海外批評北京。隨着中國經濟崛起，西方社會擔心得罪中國，即使劉霞被北京非法軟禁，也不敢公開批評，只肯在背後閉門游說，北京自然有恃無恐。他擔心類似低調、秘密的處理手法將會成為慣例。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，西方政府應該向中國政府提出外交交涉，公開批評北京軟禁劉霞是非法的，要求無條件放人，加大國際壓力。潘強調，劉霞是中國人權的標誌案例，西方社會成功救出劉霞，對內地維權人士及人權狀況都有正面作用，「所以，不再要做背後游說或閉門秘密游說，不希望劉霞再被中共非法軟禁，各國政府以及民間社會都有責任把劉霞拯救出來」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者盧燕儀  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n逝世一周年紀念　 以劉霞詩悼劉曉波　 「你說話　你說話　你說實話」"},{"pid":"0e0d86c2ef9dee226d95de9afaa3747dbbd3bee4","tid":736462,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:11:33.000Z","msg":"批評多d 仲殺多幾件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f5c53156145c2d5e6d129ccfae8de7a4db12a3","tid":736462,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:15:13.000Z","msg":"自生自滅啦<br />\n你會唔會對乞衣道友苦口婆心先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54fe8881a33dfab49dcd85f2e324a01c4029812","tid":736462,"uid":63853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:20:12.000Z","msg":"廢柴左膠一向欺善怕惡"},{"pid":"52e8f7cf4f6297510252af9f10d98bcdfd243ab1","tid":736462,"uid":66686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e54fe8881a33dfab49dcd85f2e324a01c4029812","tid":736462,"uid":63853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:20:12.000Z","msg":"廢柴左膠一向欺善怕惡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:23:05.000Z","msg":"佢地只在乎變性人去咩廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}